  - Treat the wiki as `high-signal design reference`, not as canon.
- Pages reviewed:
  - `https://grindsurvivors.wiki/beginners-guide/`
  - `https://grindsurvivors.wiki/weapons/`
  - `https://grindsurvivors.wiki/characters/`
